                            <comment id="14199839" author="ekoifman" created="Thu, 6 Nov 2014 05:45:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=hagleitn&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;hagleitn&quot;&gt;hagleitn&lt;/a&gt;, could we get this into 0.14 please?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14199891" author="thejas" created="Thu, 6 Nov 2014 06:41:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 . As discussed offline, can you also make that change to use the java path separator string instead of  &quot;:&quot; , so that it works across different OS ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14199899" author="ekoifman" created="Thu, 6 Nov 2014 06:46:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;done&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14199916" author="hagleitn" created="Thu, 6 Nov 2014 06:58:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Why did you disable precommit tests for this?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14200353" author="ekoifman" created="Thu, 6 Nov 2014 15:52:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;this is a webhcat only change, specifically around job submission. There are no unit tests that cover this&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14200790" author="hagleitn" created="Thu, 6 Nov 2014 19:54:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Alright. +1 for hive.14&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14200846" author="ekoifman" created="Thu, 6 Nov 2014 20:21:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=thejas&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;thejas&quot;&gt;thejas&lt;/a&gt; for the review.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14210848" author="thejas" created="Thu, 13 Nov 2014 19:42:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This has been fixed in 0.14 release. Please open new jira if you see any issues.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
